            <title><![CDATA[【[傻眼]#为什么吃辣椒时会同时感到辣和热#】许多人可能会好奇，为什么吃辣以后会被辣得嘴巴疼？其实，辣椒的种子没有坚硬的保护壳，当哺乳动物将辣椒吞下去咀嚼...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[傻眼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shayan-4e8000eba9.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%90%83%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E6%97%B6%E4%BC%9A%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E6%84%9F%E5%88%B0%E8%BE%A3%E5%92%8C%E7%83%AD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%90%83%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E6%97%B6%E4%BC%9A%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E6%84%9F%E5%88%B0%E8%BE%A3%E5%92%8C%E7%83%AD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么吃辣椒时会同时感到辣和热#</span></a>】许多人可能会好奇，为什么吃辣以后会被辣得嘴巴疼？其实，辣椒的种子没有坚硬的保护壳，当哺乳动物将辣椒吞下去咀嚼的时候，种子会被嚼的稀巴烂。于是有的辣椒演化出了一种叫<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E7%B4%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#辣椒素#</span></a> 的生物碱。这种生物碱能和哺乳动物体内感觉神经元的香草素受体亚型1(VR1)结合，从而产生一种灼烧的感觉。屏幕前的你，爱吃辣吗？（出品：科普中国） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4916200036040749" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hf9evzycuvj61hc0u041e02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MdGpPYholx086uloGtgk01041200qQAd0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1687756671&amp;ssig=YkMjNYQCQF&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/SKpxf4lylx086ulneM6s01041200eKDd0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1687756671&amp;ssig=bT8vxBsfA6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/LXbWuziZlx086ulmMg2c010412009JJY0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1687756671&amp;ssig=FVkkYq1dlI&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4916200036040749&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
